 \begin{pmatrix} a   &   b  \\ c   &   d \end{pmatrix} \begin{pmatrix} a   &   c  \\ b   &   d \end{pmatrix} = \begin{pmatrix} 1   &   0  \\ 0   &   1 \end{pmatrix} \qquad \Longleftrightarrow  \qquad a^2 + b^2 = c^2 + d^2 =1 \quad \text{and} \quad ac + bd = 0 \ . 
